{"tid":729573,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"願明天　能不再為妳痴纏 明白改不變　妳亦離開很遠","createTime":"2018-07-04T16:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T16:37:54.000Z","uid":71166,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d51812ebc607b627ec130e2e615308fd20146e36","tid":729573,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T16:10:39.000Z","msg":"思覺失調-劉浩龍<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RpEZVz60y-U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRpEZVz60y-U&d=GrUhjX2dZ4dhuTXPUVPuNbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=04758d04\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RpEZVz60y-U</a><br />\n<br />\n仍好嗎　重會每天失眠到　天光嗎<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大頭蝦　沒帶門匙也許很　勞氣吧<br />\n仍關心妳願每天問<br />\n最後也明白角色時已不相襯</span><br />\n還由他去代我為妳緊<br />\n<br />\n問太多根本不會講　束縛不來如人馬座<br />\n亦因愛妳令妳不安　才離開不再講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">願明天　能不再為妳痴纏<br />\n明白改不變　妳亦離開很遠<br />\n就算花光心機守每一個諾言<br />\n最後誰又會可憐<br />\n極危險　連思覺像也失調<br />\n無辦法接受現實　自製假想能延續故事<br />\n妳的聲線還仍言猶在耳　已分不清楚我位置</span><br />\n<br />\n問太多根本不會講　束縛不來如人馬座<br />\n亦因愛妳令妳不安　才離開不再講<br />\n<br />\n願明天　能不再為妳痴纏<br />\n明白改不變　妳亦離開很遠<br />\n就算花光心機守每一個諾言<br />\n最後誰又會可憐<br />\n極危險　連思覺像也失調還是我太犯賤<br />\n或是我太介意　太過膚淺<br />\n百篇短訊留言徒然又試　始終得不到妳在意<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">留低即使很多的透支<br />\n如今已做錯　記下了只有缺點<br />\n太心痛是我的一手包辦令妳心變酸<br />\n彌補如何還是太遲</span><br />\n<br />\n若然妳　如果有日說婚期<br />\n我這生福氣　也用來祝福妳<br />\n仍收起曾同渡每一齣戲飛<br />\n而這票尾　還應否捨棄"},{"pid":"be80542983de4158d08dc9308acb5b24ec8edf9b","tid":729573,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T16:11:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9092c3188bd00ca1b354ce15e16bdd10734b506","tid":729573,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T16:11:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">若然妳　如果有日說婚期<br />\n我這生福氣　也用來祝福妳<br />\n仍收起曾同渡每一齣戲飛<br />\n而這票尾　還應否捨</span>棄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"948d60c5eb5f08e5063bc1fe3ed36ca7494ebbd8","tid":729573,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be80542983de4158d08dc9308acb5b24ec8edf9b","tid":729573,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T16:11:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T16:12:04.000Z","msg":"褲妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63ff26a78d82a727c88c558d6a8558b3b181b79","tid":729573,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T16:19:03.000Z","msg":"就算花光心機守每一個諾言<br />\n最後誰又會可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"596654b8a38d2f0a941c7d4c6166c0dc016a20f2","tid":729573,"uid":170668,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T16:19:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bfedaff77b96fc0ad0cdd5a4f3c0f0ea0d441b9","tid":729573,"uid":77131,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T16:22:51.000Z","msg":"百篇短訊留言徒然又試　始終得不到妳在<br />\n意"},{"pid":"7392bc50dd1bad73a259d51cd37453a807810ae5","tid":729573,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T16:23:57.000Z","msg":"弘做咩咁感觸呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecded95170d9c8d63670f23c2a6224bce18fda76","tid":729573,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"596654b8a38d2f0a941c7d4c6166c0dc016a20f2","tid":729573,"uid":170668,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T16:19:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T16:25:48.000Z","msg":"葉兒<img src=\"/assets/f